OPTIONS rtsp://media.example.com/stream RTSP/1.0
CSeq: 1
User-Agent: ProtocolAnalyzer/1.0

RTSP/1.0 200 OK
CSeq: 1
Public: OPTIONS, DESCRIBE, SETUP, PLAY, PAUSE, TEARDOWN

